    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00371_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1877-11-09"><choice><abbr>Nov.</abbr><expan>November</expan></choice> 9, 1877.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear sir.</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I am well and hope you the same<ptr target="n0858"/> I would be very glad to see you as i did expect to come down <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="6" unit="chars"/> you <choice><orig>to day</orig><reg>today</reg></choice> or i would of wrote sooner. and if nothing <choice><sic>hapins</sic><corr>happens</corr></choice> I will be down next <choice><sic>wensday</sic><corr>Wednesday</corr></choice> night and stay until thursday night I would like very much to see you you must <choice><sic>rite</sic><corr>write</corr></choice> right <choice><sic>a way</sic><corr>away</corr></choice> and tell me how you are a getting along I would like to be with you all the time if i could i would like very much to go with you on your trip to washington. we are very <choice><sic>buisy</sic><corr>busy</corr></choice> husking just now and will be <choice><sic>fore</sic><corr>for</corr></choice> a few days and we will have nothing to do for a while)</p>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00372_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
            <p>I am in a hurry i cant <choice><sic>rite</sic><corr>write</corr></choice> any so it is <choice><sic>good by</sic><corr>goodbye</corr></choice> i hope you well</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Elmer E. Stafford</signed>
                <signed rend="right">Glendale</signed>
            <address><addrLine>To</addrLine>
                <addrLine>Walt. Whitman</addrLine>
                <addrLine>NJ</addrLine></address>
            </closer>
            
            <!--This page is endorsed, in Whitman's hand: from Elmer Stafford Nov 9 '77-->
            
        </body>
    </text>
